name: Human Resources
overview: Lovebugs, Hormone Monsters and a parade of other creatures juggle romance, workplace drama and their human clients' needs in this "Big Mouth" spinoff.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: From one-night stands to office romances, the creatures working at Human Resources have their hands — and claws — full with a new batch of humans.

tagline: Being human is hard… that’s where they come in.

episodes.name: Birth
episodes.overview: Junior Lovebug Emmy panics when she's assigned her first client: a woman who's about to go into labor. Hormone Monster Maury celebrates a big birthday.

episodes.name: Training Day
episodes.overview: After one too many romps in the break room, the Hormone Monsters are sent to sensitivity training. Walter takes Emmy on an eye-opening ride-along.

episodes.name: Bad Mummies
episodes.overview: Emmy struggles to help Becca bond with her baby, the Shame Wizard tries to impress his mom, and Connie takes care of Maury's little fellas for a day.

guest_stars.character: Tito Taylor Thomas / Kitty Dukakis / Becca's Need Demon (voice)
guest_stars.name: Maria Bamford

episodes.name: Rutgers is for Lovers
episodes.overview: Rochelle and Petra clash over whether client Nadja should pick a college based on love or ambition. Logic Rock Pete learns his office nickname.

episodes.name: Love in the Time of Postpartum
episodes.overview: Becca's return to work stirs up confusing emotions, sparking a showdown between her creatures and Barry's. Connie and Maury set Sonya up on a date.

episodes.name: The Addiction Angel
episodes.overview: As Pete and Rochelle help Doug prep for his wedding, Addiction Angel Dante throws a wrench in the plans. Joe and Gil steal one of Maury's top clients.

episodes.name: International Creature Convention
episodes.overview: Betrayals, romantic declarations and twisted schemes abound at a raucous creature convention in the skies over North Korea.

episodes.name: The Light
episodes.overview: While Maury and friends cheer on a cockfight in the back of the bar, Sonya reveals the torrid, star-crossed story behind her firing.

episodes.name: It's Almost Over
episodes.overview: As Yara's health declines, Walter and Pete scramble to fend off Keith from Grief. The feud between Emmy and Rochelle boils over at the office.

episodes.name: Shitstorm
episodes.overview: A monster hurricane forces Emmy, Rochelle and their clients to take shelter together. Meanwhile, the main office loses power — and its portals to Earth.

episodes.name: The Jizz Mitzvah
episodes.overview: At Montel's coming-of-age ceremony, the young Hormone Monster decides to do things their own way. Lovebug Emmy's new client doesn't believe in love.

episodes.name: The Tell-Tale Dick
episodes.overview: Gavin's identical twin brother, Guyvin, unsettles Lionel the Shame Wizard. Logic Rock Pete wants to tell Rochelle how he feels. Hope comes for a visit.

episodes.name: Total RePaul
episodes.overview: Dante's severed appendage haunts Pete. Lovebug Walter takes a widowed client on a couples' trip. Gil and Joe exterminate Emmy's crabs — for a bagel.

episodes.name: A League of Their Hormone
episodes.overview: The Shame Wizards play an office softball game against the Hormone Monsters. Emmy oversteps with Sarah — and Van. Rochelle and Pete finally connect.

episodes.name: Rochelle, Rochelle
episodes.overview: After Pete shares his feelings with Rochelle, Rochelle must decide if she's a Lovebug or a Hate Worm — but her decision may have ripple effects.

episodes.name: Paul Me By Your Name
episodes.overview: Walter's boyfriend Simon moves in. Paul feels conflicted about dating after his wife's death. Emmy visits the Memory Bank to dig into Sarah's mom issues.

episodes.name: Tony: The Life of an Office Cold
episodes.overview: When a cold spreads around the office, nearly all the employees get sick. But will those infected stay home and stop the spread... or continue working?

episodes.name: Pity Party
episodes.overview: Ambition Gremlin Petra helps a young client advocate for himself. Lionel throws a party to compete with Mona. Alice attends a dinner party to see Dev.

episodes.name: On the Daughterfront
episodes.overview: Paul asks Sarah to pack up her childhood bedroom, but the old house brings up painful memories. Montel tours potential colleges with their parents.
